OL,3,CChange windfall tax to make #137bn by
OL,4,C2050, Chancellor told
OL,6,FThe UK Government has previously said
OL,7,Fthe windfall tax ` which currently
OL,8,Fsits at 38% ` would be scrapped in
OL,9,F2030, or potentially earlier if oil
OL,10,Fand gas firm profits fall below a
OL,11,Fcertain level.
OL,13,FThe replacement, OEUK has said, would
OL,14,Fbe triggered by "unusually high
OL,15,Fprices" and would be levied against
OL,16,Fexcess profits.
