OL,3,CChange windfall tax to make #137bn by
OL,4,C2050, Chancellor told
OL,6,F"We are saying reform the energy
OL,7,Fprofits levy to boost national energy
OL,8,Fproduction, investment, unlock 23,000
OL,9,Fjobs, and add over #137 billion to
OL,10,Fcommunities ` or keep the tax, gain
OL,11,Fshort-term revenue, and risk the North
OL,12,FSea industry's collapse," he said.
OL,14,F"Without changes to the fiscal regime,
OL,15,FUK oil and gas could disappear within
OL,16,Fyears, not decades. That's a risk we
OL,17,Fcannot take.
