OL,3,CChange windfall tax to make #137bn by
OL,4,C2050, Chancellor told
OL,6,F"We have a range of credible sources
OL,7,Fshowing we will need between 10-15
OL,8,Fbillion barrels of oil and gas while
OL,9,Fstill meeting UK net zero goals.
OL,11,F"UK producers are only lined up to
OL,12,Fproduce about 4 billion of those, and
OL,13,Feven that target is now at risk.
OL,15,F"Today, 85% of homes are heated by
OL,16,Fgas, and while electric vehicle uptake
OL,17,Fis growing rapidly, around 23 million
OL,18,Fvehicles on our roads still rely on
OL,19,Fpetrol and diesel.
