OL,3,CChange windfall tax to make #137bn by
OL,4,C2050, Chancellor told
OL,6,F"By making the most of our homegrown
OL,7,Foil and gas while accelerating
OL,8,Frenewables, the UK can turn one of its
OL,9,Fgreatest assets ` the waters around
OL,10,Fits coast ` into a strong driver of
OL,11,Feconomic growth. We need both oil and
OL,12,Fgas and renewable energy.
OL,14,F"Changing the energy profits levy
OL,15,Fwould allow UK oil and gas operators
OL,16,Fto continue paying higher taxes when
OL,17,Fprices are high, while giving them the
OL,18,Fconfidence to invest, knowing those
OL,19,Ftaxes will adjust fairly when prices
OL,20,Fdrop."
